				<h1 class="page-header">Shift Responsibilities</h1>
				<h2>Daily:</h2>
				<ul class="howthisworkslist">
					<li>Compile a list of unanswered questions</li> 
					<li>
						Answer questions
						<ul>
							<li>No question should go unanswered for more than 3 days</li>
							<li>If needed, you can contact xsforum mentors for help with proposing an answer</li>
						</ul>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<h2>End of Shift:</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>
						Send out email to xsforumowners and cc xsforummentors:
						<ul>
							<li>List of unanswered questions with links</li>
							<li>
								Each unanswered question should have a designated category
								<table class="table table-striped table-hover table-responsive" style="width:50em">
							      <thead>
							        <tr>
							          <th>Category</th>
							          <th></th>
							        </tr>
							      </thead>
							      <tbody>
						      		<tr>
						      			<th scope="row">No idea</th>
